        <updateDate>2007-10-24T17:53:52Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Amends the Public Health Service Act to repeal provisions providing for the removal of surplus chimpanzees from a sanctuary facility. Prohibits use of such chimpanzees for research except for noninvasive behavioral studies.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
